Dehumidification This air conditioner removes excessive moisture in the room so it's ideal for high humidity conditions. Capacity With a capacity of 2 tons, this AC will cool your room in no time. Auto Restart This AC has an Auto Restart feature that automatically resumes functioning after a power outage.
